OL,3,CWhere have airport drop-off fees
OL,4,Cincreased and how can passengers avoid
OL,5,Cthem?
OL,7,FMore than three quarters of airports
OL,8,Fin the UK have introduced drop-off
OL,9,Ffees or increased them by about a
OL,10,Fthird, new data has suggested.
OL,12,FOut of 20 airports, roadside
OL,13,Fassistance service RAC found 16 of
OL,14,Fthem had hiked up what they call "kiss
OL,15,Fand fly" charges for dropping off
OL,16,Fpassengers close to the terminal.
OL,18,FITV News takes a look at where
OL,19,Fpassengers might be charged more.
OL,21,FWhich airports charge the most?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
