OL,3,CWhere have airport drop-off fees
OL,4,Cincreased and how can passengers avoid
OL,5,Cthem?
OL,7,FTwo major London airports have the
OL,8,Fhighest drop-off fees, with Gatwick
OL,9,Fcharging #10 for ten minutes and
OL,10,FStansted costing #10 for 15minutes.
OL,12,FEdinburgh and Bristol rank second,
OL,13,Fcosting #8.50 for ten minutes.
OL,15,FLondon City, which was originally the
OL,16,Fonly major UK airport to offer free
OL,17,Fdrop-offs, now has the highest rate
OL,18,Fper minute at #8 for five minutes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
