OL,3,CWhere have airport drop-off fees
OL,4,Cincreased and how can passengers avoid
OL,5,Cthem?
OL,7,FOnly four airports didn't increase
OL,8,Ftheir fees this year - Liverpool John
OL,9,FLennon, East Midlands, Belfast City
OL,10,Fand Southampton.
OL,12,FHow do the fees compare across the UK?
OL,14,FThe full list of UK airports where you
OL,15,Fhave to pay to drop off passengers is
OL,16,Fas follows:
OL,18,FWhat about taxi drop-offs?
