OL,3,CWhere have airport drop-off fees
OL,4,Cincreased and how can passengers avoid
OL,5,Cthem?
OL,7,FTravellers who book a taxi or minicab
OL,8,Fto get to the airport typically have a
OL,9,Fdrop-off fee included as part of their
OL,10,Ffare.
OL,12,FLondon black cabs might also add an
OL,13,Fauthorised extra charge directly onto
OL,14,Fthe metre.
OL,16,FHow can passengers avoid charges?
OL,18,FThere are often free drop-off options
OL,19,Favailable at airports, but these are
OL,20,Ffurther away and mean passengers must
OL,21,Fthen get a bus to the correct terminal.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
