OL,3,CWhere have airport drop-off fees
OL,4,Cincreased and how can passengers avoid
OL,5,Cthem?
OL,7,FMany airports also have public
OL,8,Ftransport connections too, which can
OL,9,Fbe a cheaper alternative.
OL,11,FDrivers are also urged to check signs
OL,12,Fcarefully at park now, pay later drop-
OL,13,Foff zones to avoid fines.
OL,15,F"Those that drop off but miss the
OL,16,Fsignage or forget to pay soon
OL,17,Fafterwards can face a parking charge
OL,18,Fnotice as high as #100," said Rod
OL,19,FDennis, a senior policy officer at the
OL,20,FRAC.
