OL,3,CWhere have airport drop-off fees
OL,4,Cincreased and how can passengers avoid
OL,5,Cthem?
OL,7,FDennis said he was disappointed to see
OL,8,Fairports charging so much for dropping
OL,9,Foff family and friends.
OL,11,FHe continued: "Of course, airports
OL,12,Fneed to manage the limited space they
OL,13,Fhave carefully, but if free,
OL,14,Fconvenient drop-off zones work at many
OL,15,Fother international airports, then why
OL,16,Fnot here?"
