OL,3,CWhere have airport drop-off fees
OL,4,Cincreased and how can passengers avoid
OL,5,Cthem?
OL,7,FWhy do airports charge drop-off fees?
OL,9,FA spokesperson for airport trade
OL,10,Fassociation AirportsUK said the fees
OL,11,Fare "part of the airport business
OL,12,Fmodel and help support the provision
OL,13,Fof the widest variety of flights from
OL,14,Fthe airport".
OL,16,FThey said they help manage congestion,
OL,17,Ftraffic, and pollution to meet climate
OL,18,Fchange objectives, issues that
OL,19,F"airports are mandated to manage by
OL,20,Fthe Government and local authorities".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
