OL,3,CWhere have airport drop-off fees
OL,4,Cincreased and how can passengers avoid
OL,5,Cthem?
OL,7,FCould the government change airport
OL,8,Ffees?
OL,10,FConservative peer Lord Moylan is
OL,11,Fcalling for a review of "scandalously
OL,12,Fexcessive" drop-off charges and hopes
OL,13,Fto amend the Civil Aviation Bill.
OL,15,FThe legislation, which aims to reform
OL,16,Faviation laws and strengthen passenger
OL,17,Frights, particularly looking at
OL,18,Fdisability access, passed its third
OL,19,Freading in the House of Lords and will
OL,20,Fbe debated by MPs.
OL,26,@sD@YOUtD@JO]
