OL,3,CWhere have airport drop-off fees
OL,4,Cincreased and how can passengers avoid
OL,5,Cthem?
OL,7,F"This Bill is focused on strengthening
OL,8,Fconsumer rights and protections,
OL,9,Freforming aviation regulation and
OL,10,Fenhancing aviation safety," transport
OL,11,Fminister Lord Hendy of Richmond Hill
OL,12,Fsaid.
